Source: service-provider-canopen-protocol
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Robert Burger <robert.burger@dlr.de>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), autotools-dev
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Section: libs
Homepage: https://www.burger-system.de/robotkernel/service_provider_canopen_protocol
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/robotkernel-hal/service_provider_canopen_protocol.git
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/robotkernel-hal/service_provider_canopen_protocol.git
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: service-provider-canopen-protocol-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: robotkernel-dev (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Robotkernel service provider to export CANOpen dictionary access services.
  This service provider gains unified access to CANOpen dictionaries of robotkernel
  modules. It support retreaving of object dictionary lists, read objects, read and write
  object elements.

